text: Naima El-Rhouati (born 19 July 1976) is a Moroccan gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Moroccan female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Morocco Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
